它气势宏大，是最具有影响力的民族品牌。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;冬青黑体简体中文 W3&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;华人酒纯粮酿造，独具风格，它晶莹剔透，酒体丰满，厚重圆润，入口绵纯，回味悠长，芳香四溢，沁人心碑。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;冬青黑体简体中文 W3&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;华人酒&rdquo;品牌已经国家工商总局注册，包装已经国家工商总局专利局批准为专利，是最具中华民族和华人的特色及形象。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;冬青黑体简体中文 W3&quot;, 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 0px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;华人酒被酒业内外誉为&ldquo;中华瑰宝&rdquo;，廿一世纪，华人世界，在华人的世界就要彰